Package com.navis.framework.persistence.queryexecution

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EntityColumnCalculator
    Calculates number of table columns for a given entity.
    HeavyQueryHandler
    Detector and handler for potentially heavy domain queries.
    HqlQueryCreator
    Creates an Hql query.
    HqlQueryExecutor
    Executes an Hql query.
    HqlStringCreator
    Creates Hql strings from a DomainQuery.
    HqlTypesValuesConverter
    A converter of types and values from a DomainQuery to a Query.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultEntityColumnCalculator
    Default implementation to calculate the number of columns for a given entity class name.
    DefaultHeavyQueryHandler
    Default implementation to detect heavy queries.
    DefaultHqlQueryCreator
    Bottleneck class to create a Hibernate Query from a DomainQuery.
    DefaultHqlQueryExecutor
    Executes an HQL query.
    DefaultHqlStringCreator
    Creates the HQL from a DomainQuery.
    DefaultHqlTypesValuesConverter
    Converter for types and values from a DomainQuery to the format needed by Query.
    HqlQueryCreationResult
    This class represents the result of Hibernate Query creation.
    HqlStringCreationResult
    Represent the result of a HQL string creation.
    QueryExecution
    This class represent the result of a Hibernate Query execution.
    ResultHolder
    Used internally to encapsulate all of the artifacts of query execution
    TypesValuesConversionResult
    The result of a types and values conversion of a domain query.
  • Enum Summary
